{"text_id":177496,"tokens":["This"," paper"," investigates"," the"," problem"," of"," power"," allocation"," for"," discrete","-","input"," delay","-","limited"," fading"," channels","."," The"," main"," focus"," is"," on"," the"," design"," of"," power"," allocation"," strategies"," that"," maximize"," the"," average"," mutual"," information"," (","AMI",")"," under"," a"," long","-","term"," power"," constraint","."," We"," first"," derive"," the"," optimal"," power"," allocation"," policy"," in"," the"," high"," signal","-","to","-","noise"," ratio"," (","SNR",")"," regime","."," Then",","," we"," propose"," a"," low","-","complexity"," sub","optimal"," power"," allocation"," algorithm"," for"," the"," entire"," SNR"," range","."," The"," proposed"," algorithm"," is"," based"," on"," the"," principle"," of"," '","water","-","filling","'"," and"," is"," shown"," to"," perform"," close"," to"," the"," optimal"," policy"," in"," the"," high"," SNR"," regime","."," We"," also"," provide"," numerical"," results"," to"," validate"," the"," theoretical"," analysis"," and"," to"," demonstrate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," the"," proposed"," algorithm","."," The"," results"," show"," that"," the"," proposed"," power"," allocation"," strategy"," significantly"," improves"," the"," AMI"," over"," the"," equal"," power"," allocation"," strategy",","," especially"," in"," the"," high"," SNR"," regime","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4","label":1}